<br>
Just go do the quest the way I outlined it on the first page of this thread. Trust me. That'll fix essentially every problem you ever have in Freeport, except for the evil guilds in the sewers...<br>
<br>
Sure, you can Rp your heart out, slaying every Freeport Militia member you encounter, but really, it's a hassle. You can't get to the Arena, you can't go take the boat, you can't wander around about 5 different zones for fear of accidentally encountering a guard who hits for 175+...<br>
<br>
/shrug<br>
<br>
Oh, and I soloed Sergeant Slate yesterday. I've owed him that for quite some time now. Nearly 2 years ago, he KS'd literally every mob I could find while trying to get from level 3 to 4 in EC. As a result, getting from 3 to 4 took me over 8 hours. (And all you newer EQ members, this was long before the mob spawn rate was upped in EC, and long before light blue exp, and long long before the &quot;easy road to level 10&quot; system was in place.....)<br>
<br>
Basically I would fight a mob down to the last few hits, then Slate would run up and hit it for 175 and KS me every single time. Then I'd be battered, go sit down and try to heal, and guess who'd be there when a new fire beetle or black bear spawned nearby? Yep, Slate. He's whack them and move on....It was because of him that I went to Greater Faydark and Crushbone at that level... Ah good old Orc Hill.....<br>
<br>
The sad part is that I was forced to use 2 Soulfire charges to beat Slate. I see they've buffed up his abilities ever since the AA system was added. Yeah, why would you think that having AA points would actually make the game easier, when they just buff all the mobs to compensate? Bah.<br>
<br>
/shrug<br>
<br>
<br>
Oh well, bye. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub110.ezboard.com/uotterantilles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Otter Antilles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(6/7/02 9:38:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=419.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: nobody ever listens to Scaldar..</span><hr size=1> Sorry for the inconvience, Scaldar... I guess it's too much to ask you to stand by the oaths you took to get that Soulfire you carry.<br>
<br>
I guess just trying to RP the little bit this game let me was just an inconvience that I was willing to live with.<br>
<br>
Why should I treat EFP and WFP as any different than Kael?  They are both full of beings that differ in opinion from the way my toon does.  There are plenty of other arenas to fight in, plenty of other banks and vendors to use, plenty of other ways to get from point A to point B (you can still use the boat... just have to learn creative ways to get to it).<br>
<br>
Killing all of the militia-men was one of my favorite pasttimes in EQ... it's one of the main reasons I was bound 75% of the time in Freeport.<br>
<br>
Oh yeah, have to agree with you about Slate... he died the first time I thought I could solo him way back when, and I continually looked for him any time I was in EC. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showPrevMessage?topicID=419.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showNextMessage?topicID=419.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=419.topic&index=24><img src=http://www.unbeliever.net/images/lanys/postreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.emailToFriend?topicID=419.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.threadControl?topicID=419.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=419.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub110.ezboard.com/feqasylumpaladin.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=419.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub110.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eqasylumgeneral">General<option value="eqasylumfrm33">Luclin Info<option value="eqasylumfrm25">Raid Discussions<option 